  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  preterm and full-term infants in the NICU requiring a percutaneous central venous
             catheter

          -  ventilatory support in the form of conventional ventilation, Continuous Positive Air
             Pressure (CPAP) or High Frequency Oscillation(HFO)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  seizures

          -  receiving muscle relaxants

          -  skin disorders causing disruption of stratum corneum
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
